                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271025-174-off1004 t18271025-174-cd1005"></join>, 1 umbrella, value 25s., and 1 handkerchief, value 5s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18271025-174-victim893" type="victimName">
                        Edward Reddish Thomas 
                        Blyth
                     <interp inst="t18271025-174-victim893" type="surname" value="Blyth"></interp>
